OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1779120674
OL,3,CCafe employing adults with learning
OL,4,Cdisabilities up for second award
OL,6,FA social enterprise cafe has been
OL,7,Fnominated for its second award, for
OL,8,Fits outreach work in the community.
OL,10,FHartnell's Cafe employs five adults
OL,11,Fwith learning disabilities - for many
OL,12,Fit's their first ever job.
OL,14,FRichard Graham is one of the residents
OL,15,Fat Trinity Lodge, a service for adults
OL,16,Fwith learning disabilities and complex
OL,17,Fneeds, who works at the cafe.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1779120674
OL,3,CCafe employing adults with learning
OL,4,Cdisabilities up for second award
OL,6,FHe said he was 'happy' and 'proud'
OL,7,Fwhen he found out he got a job, and
OL,8,Ffor Richard it was his first job at
OL,9,Fthe age of 64.
OL,11,FHe said: "I was quite happy and proud.
OL,13,F"I just love it. I dish up the soup
OL,14,Fonto the plate. Put the plates in the
OL,15,Fdishwasher."
OL,17,FAmanda Jackson, one of the chefs,
OL,18,Fworks side by side with Richard.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1779120674
OL,3,CCafe employing adults with learning
OL,4,Cdisabilities up for second award
OL,6,FShe said: "It's been amazing. They're
OL,7,Faccepted. People come up to the
OL,8,Fcounter all the time to speak to the
OL,9,Fresidents.
OL,11,F"It's been brilliant, they are proud,
OL,12,Fso proud, I'm like a proud parent."
OL,14,FTrinity House and Lodge is a finalist
OL,15,Fin the community outreach category of
OL,16,Fthe Housing with Care Awards, in
OL,17,Frecognition of its work through
OL,18,FHartnell's Cafe.
OL,26,@zD@Orr
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/6
