OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1779120674
OL,3,CCafe employing adults with learning
OL,4,Cdisabilities up for second award
OL,6,FLorraine Platt, the service manager
OL,7,Fsaid: "I was shocked because I still
OL,8,Fdon't know who nominated us, so I was
OL,9,Freally surprised.
OL,11,F"I had to have an interview so I could
OL,12,Ffully explain how we reached out to
OL,13,Fcommunity and the part we play in
OL,14,Fcommunity. It means our work is
OL,15,Frecognised."
OL,17,FIt's estimated that employment rates
OL,18,Ffor people with learning disabilities
OL,19,Fin Scotland are between four and eight
OL,20,Fpercent, according to the Scottish
OL,21,Fgovernment.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1779120674
OL,3,CCafe employing adults with learning
OL,4,Cdisabilities up for second award
OL,6,FIn response, Lorraine added: "It
OL,7,Fshocks me, it saddens me.
OL,9,F"We've recently employed a young man
OL,10,Fwho told me in the interview that he
OL,11,Ffelt he'd never been appreciated, that
OL,12,Fhe'd been used for free labour."
OL,14,FLoyal customers are hoping the cafe
OL,15,Fwill bring home the award.
OL,17,FOne customer said: "I do enjoy meeting
OL,18,Fthe residents when they are serving
OL,19,Fbecause you can tell they enjoy it."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
