CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1779120674
OL,3,CCafe employing adults with learning
OL,4,Cdisabilities up for second award
OL,6,FAnother explained: "Absolutely
OL,7,Famazing, they really do deserve it. It
OL,8,Freally is a recourse for the
OL,9,Fcommunity."
OL,11,FThe winner will be announced in London
OL,12,Fof June 5th.
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
